---

---

<div class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100">
  {/* Background */}
  <div class="pointer-events-none fixed inset-0 -z-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900/40 via-slate-950 to-black" />
    <div class="absolute -top-40 left-1/2 h-72 w-72 -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 blur-3xl" />
  </div>

  <main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    {/* Hero */}
    <section class="text-center space-y-5">
      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-slate-900/80 border border-cyan-500/30 text-xs font-medium text-cyan-300">
        Support LikeC4
        <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 animate-pulse" />
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">
        Power Open Architecture-as-Code
      </h1>

      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        LikeC4 is an independent, open source toolkit for modeling and visualizing real-world systems as code. Your
        sponsorship funds real feature work, maintenance, and a healthy ecosystem to rely on.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 pt-2">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/likec4"
          class="
            inline-flex items-center
            px-5 py-2.5
            rounded-xl
            bg-cyan-500 text-slate-950
            font-medium no-underline
            hover:bg-cyan-400
            transition
            shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/20
          "
        >
          Become a sponsor
        </a>
        <!-- <a
          href="https://github.com/likec4/likec4/discussions"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-600 text-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-900/70 transition"
        >
          View roadmap
        </a> -->
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Why sponsor */}
    <section class="mt-16 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Why sponsor LikeC4?</h2>

      <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50 mb-1">
            Serious tooling, independent project
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            A focused Architecture-as-Code toolkit used to model and visualize complex systems without click-drag
            theater.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50 mb-1">
            High leverage for your teams
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            Clear diagrams, shared understanding, better reviews, smoother onboarding, and documentation that stays in
            sync.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/80 border border-slate-800/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-50 mb-1">
            Built and maintained by practitioners
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
            Sponsorship turns nights and weekends into structured, reliable work on features, fixes, and integrations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Impact */}
    <section class="mt-16 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What your support makes possible</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
        Sponsorship is a direct input into LikeC4 improvements, not a vague fund.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
          <li>
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
            Core features: manual layouts, deployment views, dynamic and sequence views, better layout algorithms.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
            Performance and stability for large models and real world architectures.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
            Tooling: VS Code extension, CLI, Docker images, embedding in docs and internal portals.
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
          <li>
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
            AI and MCP friendly context so your architecture is machine readable without extra work.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
            Documentation, guides, and examples that teams can adopt without hand-holding.
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="text-cyan-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
            Keeping the core open and accessible for individuals and teams everywhere.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Tiers */}
    <section class="mt-16 space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Sponsor tiers</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
        Choose a level that matches how much value your team gets from LikeC4. All sponsors are credited unless you opt
        out.
      </p>

      <div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
        {/* Supporter */}
        <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/90 border border-slate-800/90">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">‚òï Supporter</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">from $5 / month</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            For individuals and curious engineers.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-300 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Optional name in the sponsors list</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {/* Contributor */}
        <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/90 border border-slate-800/90">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">üß© Contributor</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">from $25 / month</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            For regular users who want LikeC4 to keep evolving.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-300 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Name or handle listed</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Occasional early previews and RFC pings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {/* Team Sponsor */}
        <div class="relative p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/95 border border-cyan-500/50 shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/15">
          <div class="absolute -top-2 right-3 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-500/20 border border-cyan-400/60 text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wide text-cyan-300">
            Recommended
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">üèóÔ∏è Team Sponsor</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-300">from $100 / month</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            For teams that use LikeC4 in real workflows and want a healthy project.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-300 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Company logo and link on this page</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Priority attention on bugs and integrations via GitHub</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Input into feature priorities through private discussions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        {/* Partner */}
        <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-900/90 border border-slate-800/90">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg">üöÄ Partner</h3>
            <span class="text-xs text-slate-400">$500+ / month</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            For organizations who see LikeC4 as part of their strategic tooling stack.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-300 space-y-1">
            <li>‚Ä¢ Prominent logo placement</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Option for joint case study or quote</li>
            <li>‚Ä¢ Direct line for roadmap alignment and feedback</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-2">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sponsors/likec4"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-cyan-500 text-slate-950 font-medium hover:bg-cyan-400 transition"
        >
          Sponsor LikeC4 on GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    {/* Current sponsors */}
    <section class="mt-16 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Current sponsors</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300">
        These people and teams help keep LikeC4 actively maintained and independent.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 gap-5 items-center justify-items-center bg-slate-950/60 border border-slate-800/80 rounded-2xl p-5">
        {/* Replace with dynamic list from GitHub Sponsors API or manual entries */}
        <div class="w-24 h-8 rounded-md bg-slate-800/80 animate-pulse" />
        <div class="w-24 h-8 rounded-md bg-slate-800/80 animate-pulse" />
        <div class="w-24 h-8 rounded-md bg-slate-800/80 animate-pulse" />
        <div class="w-24 h-8 rounded-md bg-slate-800/80 animate-pulse" />
      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">
        Want your logo here as a Team Sponsor or Partner? Become a sponsor on GitHub and reach out.
      </p>
    </section>

    {/* Final CTA */}
    <section class="mt-16 mb-8 text-center space-y-3">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
        If LikeC4 replaces proprietary tools or saves your team time, help support it.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Sponsorship keeps the project fast, reliable, and focused on real engineering needs instead of marketing
        checklists.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/sponsors/likec4"
        class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-2.5 rounded-xl bg-cyan-500 text-slate-950 font-semibold hover:bg-cyan-400 transition shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/20"
      >
        Become a sponsor
      </a>
    </section>
  </main>
</div>
